Module roborallyGUI
Package model

Class DataModelManager

java.lang.Object
model.DataModelManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
DataModel
public class DataModelManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataModel
This class represents the DataModel of the RoboRallys Client Side. The Data here gets manipulated either by the Server through the Client/Server Architecture or by the various ViewModels. The Data here updates the various ViewModels, thus the Views and sends Data to the Server through the Client/Server Architecture

      public void updateViewModels()
